These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola
There 2 different types of food: grapes, cauliflower
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola  | coffee |
| Food       | grapes | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | badminton     | rugby  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, malaysian
1. the thai is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the thai is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | zombie  |
| Nationality   | thai | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
