.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, dutch
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird
1. the dutch is on the left or right of the australian##3
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | australian | dutch |
| Pet           | bird     | chinchilla  |

