.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, photographer
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | dancing |
| Job     | writer        | photographer |

